sequenceDiagram
    actor Player as Player
    participant SWA as React SPA
    participant API as .NET 10 API
    participant MSID as Microsoft Identity
    participant DB as SQLite
    participant KV as Key Vault

    Note over API,KV: Startup — secrets bootstrap
    API->>KV: GetSecrets (Managed Identity)
    KV-->>API: ClientId, AppInsights connection string

    Note over Player,MSID: Auth Flow — Microsoft OAuth2
    Player->>SWA: Open app
    SWA->>MSID: Redirect GET /auth/login (OAuth2 code flow)
    MSID-->>Player: Microsoft login prompt
    Player->>MSID: Credentials
    MSID-->>SWA: Auth code at /auth/callback
    SWA->>API: POST /api/auth/callback (exchange code)
    API->>MSID: Validate JWT Bearer token
    MSID-->>API: Token claims (userId, name)
    API-->>SWA: Set DevCookie + 200 OK

    Note over Player,DB: Game Stats — Save Result
    Player->>SWA: Completes game (Win/Loss/Draw)
    SWA->>API: PUT /api/{game}/players/{id}/stats (Bearer JWT)
    API->>DB: Upsert PlayerStats + DifficultyStats (Easy/Medium/Hard)
    DB-->>API: Updated record
    API-->>SWA: 200 OK + PlayerStats JSON

    Note over Player,DB: Leaderboard — View Rankings
    Player->>SWA: Open leaderboard tab
    SWA->>API: GET /api/{game}/statistics/leaderboard
    Note right of API: Rate limit: 10 req/min/IP (fixed window)
    API->>DB: SELECT top 10 by TotalWins
    DB-->>API: Ranked player records
    API-->>SWA: JSON leaderboard array

    Note over Player,API: Real-time Multiplayer — SignalR
    Player->>API: WS connect /api/hubs/lobby (JWT auth required)
    API-->>Player: Lobby state + available rooms
    Player->>API: Join or create room
    API-->>Player: Room joined → redirect to /api/hubs/multiplayer
    API-->>Player: Real-time game events (moves, turns, results)
    API-->>Player: Win/Loss recorded + stats trigger PUT
